      "value": "<div class=\"content\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<h2>Wortha, Trashmother [N] <a id=\"toc-wortha\"></a><a id=\"toc-wortha-217\"></a></h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item d-flex flex-wrap\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"flex-even column\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<p>The closest goblins get to a deity of civilisation and progress, Wortha is the guiding force behind the goblinâ€™s rise to a level of culture above a hunting pack.</p>\n<p><strong>Edicts</strong> seek new knowledge and techniques, be of use to a wider community, guard children from harm<br /><strong>Anathema</strong> refuse to acknowledge or learn from mistakes, rely on the charity of others for extended periods, throw something away if it still has use<br /><strong>Follower Alignments</strong> NG, LN, N, CN, NE</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"content\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<h3>Devotee Benefits</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item d-flex flex-wrap\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"flex-even column\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Divine Font</strong> <em>heal</em></p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Divine Skill</strong> Crafting</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Favored Weapon</strong> polytool</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Domains</strong> creation, earth, family, knowledge</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Cleric Spells</strong> 1st: <em>temporary tool</em>, 3rd: <em>hypercognition</em>, 4th: <em>creation</em></p>\n</div>\n</div>"
